tagline: A useful utility developed with Tier 2 agents in mind.
body:
##- Teir 2 Agent Utility -##

**Lead Developer**: SparksD2145@GitHub

A useful tool written for (PACE) Tier 2 Agents to assist in performing basic functions of Tier 2 representatives, primarily with a focus in accessing/launching necessary tools. Provides modular accessibility to add/remove your own commands, as well as drop-in extension support.

Currently use-at-your-own-risk software pending appoval.  Please do not redistribute this basic batch script, trying to limit availability.  Download your own copy and extensions to match, don't provide a copy to your neighbor. Thanks!
name: Tier 2 Agent Utility
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
